-- Haitong Securities First-Half Profit Declines 27.2% as Revenue Falls 4.33%
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-08T22:58:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-08/haitong-securities-first-half-profit-declines-27-2-as-revenue-falls-4-33-.html

          
          
             Haitong Securities Co. said first-
half net income fell 27.2 percent from a year earlier to 1.78
billion yuan ($263 million), according to a statement to
Shanghai’s stock exchange.  
 The brokerage’s first-half revenue fell 4.33 percent to
3.66 billion yuan, according to the statement.  
 Haitong’s profit in June was 484.9 million yuan on sales of
902.8 million yuan, the company said, without giving comparative
monthly figures.  
